reviews.review_text: SOUND THE AIR RAID ALARM!!!!!!!!!!!! Great sounding Aud! TONS of Phil bombs and low end! Fall 85' tour was EPIC!!!!!!!!!!!!!!

Best of the bunch My 1st Dead show.  I was 16.  I left my stash back at the house by accident.  Kind soul in the lot, hooked me up with 10$ worth of bud for the show.  Dumpy sounding place, but this is the best of the auds.  Quite listenable.
